    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Collections of historical records and primary source documents that have accumulated over the course of an individual's or organization's lifetime, and are kept to show the function or history of the person or an organization. Documents may be tangible or digital.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
